      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's looking for someone who will love it just as much. It's spotless inside and out, totally ready for your next adventure. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
