    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features a fully serviced double-VANOS system and synchronized individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis integrity is peerless, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec suspension geometry that preserves its surgical handling characteristics. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the original variable M differential lock. Every mechanical component, from the cooling system to the bushing tolerances, remains in peak operational condition, making this a turnkey specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
