    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is flawless, treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the deep metallic finish pop under any light\u2014no swirls, no rock chips, and absolutely no imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium hand-stitched leather seats show zero signs of wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, dial, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It has been serviced exclusively at the certified dealership with a comprehensive paper trail documenting every scheduled oil change and multi-point inspection. With incredibly low mileage and a chassis that has never seen salt or snow, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or an enthusiast to own a truly flawless example of automotive excellence. It comes with all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover. Inspection-ready and prepared for its next fastidious owner.",
      "price": 48500.0,
